Insider Activity


Individual




Michael Raymond Burns



Mr. Michael R. Burns is Independent Director at Hasbro, Inc. and Chairman at NOVICA United, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Hasbro, Inc., Lions Gate Entertainment Corp., CinemaNow Ltd., and TV Guide Entertainment Group.
Mr. Burns was previously employed as a Managing Director & Head-Investment Banking by Prudential Securities and Chairman by Ignite! Entertainment. He also served on the board at Nextpoint GP LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from Arizona State University and an MBA from the University of California, Los Angeles.



