Michael Raymond Burns, MBA

Age : 58Public asset : 56,894,356 USDLinked companies :  Hasbro, Inc. -  Lions Gate Entertainment Corp. (USA) 





Summary 



Mr. Michael R. Burns is Member-Board of Visitors at UCLA Anderson School of Management.He is on the Board of Directors at Hasbro, Inc., Lions Gate Entertainment Corp., CinemaNow Ltd. and TV Guide Entertainment Group. Mr. Burns was previously employed as Chairman by NOVICA United, Inc., Managing Director & Head-Investment Banking by Prudential Securities, and Chairman by Ignite! Entertainment.He also served on the board at Nextpoint GP LLC.He received his undergraduate degree from Arizona State University and an MBA from UCLA Anderson School of Management.



